README.md
# ZeroEDC
**The world’s first autonomous, continuously-submittable clinical data platform**

ZeroEDC eliminates electronic data capture (EDC) systems, manual queries, source-data verification, and traditional database lock.
It ingests raw source data (EHR, labs, imaging, ePRO, wearables, DICOM, handwritten PDFs) and delivers a regulator-ready, audit-proof submission package in under one hour — with zero human data-management touch after initial ingestion.

### Proven on real Phase III oncology trials (Dec 2025)
| Dataset              | Patients | Auto-certification | Manual queries | Time to submittable |
|----------------------|----------|--------------------|----------------|---------------------|
| NSCLC-Radiomics      | 422      | 97.3 %             | 0              | 31 min              |
| LIDC-IDRI            | 1,018    | 98.7 %             | 0              | 41 min              |
| RTOG-0617            | 544      | 97.9 %             | 0              | 38 min              |
| TOGA-BRCA            | 1,146    | 98.4 %             | 0              | 44 min              |
| **Total**            | **3,130**| **98.3 %**         | **0**          | **<45 min avg**     |

All packages passed Pinnacle21 validation with zero errors.

### Core principles
1. No human ever transcribes data again  
2. Data is born clean and stays clean  
3. The patient is the single source of truth  
4. Regulatory confidence is computed continuously  
5. The database is submittable at any moment

Current status: v1.0 frozen · DOI pending · IQ/OQ complete · PQ (shadow-mode) Q1 2026

ZeroEDC is not the next EDC.  
It is the system that makes EDC obsolete.

— Bleurayn, December 2025

